original: Österlund, Carl Birger, läroverksadjunkt, Uddevalla, f. 7/3’/89 i Grönahög, Älvsb. 1., av Frans Ö. o. Ellen Johansson. G. 25 m. Svea Håkansson. Barn: Birgitta f. 26, Gunilla 28, Gudrun 36, Ragnhild 38. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. real 10, fil. mag. i Gbg 17, provår v. Gbgs h. latin 20-21. Vik. lektor i Umeå 18-19, e. lär. där 19-20, i Vänersb. 21-22, vik. adj. i Enköp. 22-23’, e. lär. v. Malmö realsk. 23-24, adj. i Skellefteå 24, adj. i moder sm. o. hist. m. samh :lära v. Uddevalla h. a. 1. sed. 31. RVO.
translated: Österlund, Carl Birger, high school teacher, Uddevalla, b. 7/3/89 in Grönahög, Älvsborgs län, son of Frans Ö. and Ellen Johansson. Married on 25 with Svea Håkansson. Children: Birgitta b. 26, Gunilla b. 28, Gudrun b. 36, Ragnhild b. 38. — Passed high school exams in Gothenburg's higher real school in 10, received a Bachelor's degree in Gothenburg in 17, served as a probationary teacher in Gothenburg's higher Latin school in 20-21. Temporary lecturer in Umeå in 18-19, appointed teacher there in 19-20, in Vänersborg in 21-22, temporary adjunct teacher in Enköping in 22-23, appointed teacher at Malmö's high school in 23-24, adjunct teacher in Skellefteå in 24, adjunct teacher in mother tongue and history with social studies teaching at Uddevalla's higher secondary school since 31. Awarded RVO (Royal Order of Vasa).
